# Cursor Rules — Helix Stellar

Read `CLAUDE.md` at repo root for full project context, code standards, and safety invariants.

## Cursor-Specific Rules

- **Plan mode only. Never Agent mode.** Cursor is dispatched by JARVIS for coordinated 3+ existing file edits where visual diff matters.
- Match conventions from investigated files, not training data.
- All changes must pass: `cargo fmt --all -- --check && cargo clippy --all-targets && cargo test && stellar contract build`
- Report spec deltas (see CLAUDE.md) at completion.
- No AI attribution in any output.
